reviewText: Great dvd!!!  Marvelous movie and theater career of an extraordinary performer told.
One of the great actresses of our time; this is a wonderful overview, for those who don't know anything about her.
Very good synopsis of Kathrine Hepburn's life and career, but is not updated to her death in June of 2003.  The DVD is a bit short, but still informing.
I like the actress...so I enjoyed what I learned about her life.  It was well-done and tasteful.
